snippet.title: I Am Fish - Official Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Reunite fish friends in this physics-based game, I Am Fish, available now for Xbox Series X/S, Xbox One, PC, and Xbox Game Pass.

I Am Fish tells the story of four fish friends trying to reunite after being forcibly separated and scattered throughout the coastal county of Barnardshire. Watch the I Am Fish launch trailer to see these fishy friends in action.

#IGN #Gaming #IAmFish
